Title: Wspolczesne problemy rozwoju administracji publicznej w Polsce/Contemporary Problems of Public Administration in Poland 
Abstract: The article focusses on a critical analysis of basic problems that contemporary administration faces in the
course of its transformation. The Author has stressed the role of the tendency of economize, citizen participation
and deregulation of law. The Author has also shown how the reforms of the Polish administration reflect general
globalization and europeization tendencies. He has also distinguished certain paculiarities of the Polish administrative
transformation.     
